OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Feasing to leave a dry night with clear
OL,7,Fspells and light winds, allowing a
OL,8,Flittle shallow mist or fog to form in
OL,9,Fplaces. Rather warm and muggy,
OL,10,Fespecially in urban areas towards the
OL,11,Fsouth.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FMostly dry and bright on
OL,14,FMonday with sunny spells for all. The
OL,15,Fodd isolated shower is possible in the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Feeling hot and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
